19 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 34.301, as
20 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 134, O.S.L. 2023 (62 O.S. Supp.
21 2024, Section 34.301), is amended to read as follows:
22 Section 34.301. A. This act shall be known and may be cited as
23 the "Civil Service and Human Capital Modernization Act".
